1. *Kafu* mi je ukusna. (The coffee tastes good.)
2. *Kafe* je za mnoge ljude nezamisliv bez njega. (Coffee is unimaginable for many people without it.)
3. Kupio sam *kafu* za svoju ukućanku. (I bought coffee for my family.)
4. On je preporučio da se za izlazak ponese *kafa*. (He suggested bringing coffee for the outing.)
5. Ona voli da popije *kafu* ujutro. (She likes to have coffee in the morning.)
6. *Kafa* je jedna od najpopularnijih pića na svetu. (Coffee is one of the most popular drinks in the world.)